          <div class="slot">
            <div class="time">Morning</div>
            <div class="title">Check out and store bags</div>
            <div class="why">
              They check out at the Wyndham, leave bags with bell services, and move
              to the Strip without clock stress.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="slot">
            <div class="time">About 10:00 am to 11:15 am</div>
            <div class="title">Brunch at Mon Ami Gabi, Paris Las Vegas</div>
            <div class="why">
              Outdoor French bistro style brunch facing the Bellagio fountains. This is
              one of the most pleasant brunch settings in Vegas and fits perfectly before
              an early afternoon flight.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="slot">
            <div class="time">Late morning</div>
            <div class="title">Short stroll on the Strip and photos</div>
            <div class="why">
              They can walk a little, take final pictures, and soak in the last bit of
              Vegas before heading to the airport.
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
